def test_business_like_collect(self):
        try:
            # 初始化发现页操作类（传入self即可复用所有minium对象）
            find_page = FindPage(self)

            # 链式调用公共方法，逻辑清晰
            find_page.goto_find_page()

            self.page.wait_for(
                lambda: self.page.element_is_exists(menu_element, max_timeout=max_timeout),
                max_timeout=max_timeout)
            time.sleep(3)

            # 需要判断是不是在商务菜单
            menu_name = self.page.get_element(menu_active_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            menu_name_text = menu_name.text


            if menu_name_text != menu_business_name:
                menu_list = self.page.get_elements(menu_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                # 点击商务
                for i in menu_list:
                    if i.text == menu_business_name:
                        i.tap()

            cur_menu_name = self.page.get_element(menu_active_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            if cur_menu_name.text == menu_business_name:
                self.logger.info(f"已切换到 {menu_business_name} 菜单")
            else:
                self.logger.info(f"菜单切换失败，当前菜单为： {cur_menu_name.text} ")

            # 显式等待
            self.page.wait_for(
                lambda: self.page.element_is_exists(business_list_one_element, max_timeout=max_timeout),
                max_timeout=max_timeout)

            # 点击列表的第一条商务供需
            business_list_one = self.page.get_element(business_list_one_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            business_list_one.tap()

            # 判断是否跳转至 商务供需详情页
            # 初始化重试次数
            retry_count = 0
            success = False
            max_retry_times = 3  # 最大重试次数

            if self.app.current_page != find_business_detail_page_url:
                # 循环重试（最多3次）
                while retry_count <= max_retry_times:
                    try:
                        self.logger.info(f"第 {retry_count + 1} 次尝试跳转到商务供需详情页...")

                        # 执行跳转（等待URL变更）
                        self.app.go_to(url=find_business_detail_page_url, is_wait_url_change=True)

                        # 关键：正确判断当前页面路径（需取path属性）
                        current_path = self.app.current_page.path
                        if current_path == find_business_detail_page_url:
                            self.logger.info("进入商务供需详情页成功！")
                            success = True
                            break  # 成功则退出循环
                        else:
                            self.logger.warning(f"跳转后页面不符，当前路径：{current_path}，目标路径：{find_business_detail_page_url}")

                    except Exception as e:
                        self.logger.error(f"第 {retry_count + 1} 次跳转失败：{str(e)}")

                    # 重试次数+1，失败则短暂休眠后重试
                    retry_count += 1
                    if retry_count <= max_retry_times:
                        time.sleep(1)  # 休眠1秒避免频繁重试

                # 最终结果判断
                if not success:
                    self.logger.error("进入商务供需详情页失败（已重试3次）...")

                # 显式等待
                self.page.wait_for(
                    lambda: self.page.element_is_exists(dynamic_comment_add_element,max_timeout=max_timeout),
                    max_timeout=max_timeout)

            """点赞 like"""
            like_status = self.page.get_element(business_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            # 先判断是否是 未点赞
            if like_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_unlike_icon_src]:
                # 如果是未点赞 先点赞 like
                unlike_icon = self.page.get_element(business_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                unlike_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_like_status = self.page.get_element(business_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_like_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_like_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_unlike_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_unlike_icon_name} 失败")

                time.sleep(1)

            else:
                # 如果是已点赞 取消点赞
                like_icon = self.page.get_element(business_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                like_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_like_status = self.page.get_element(business_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_like_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_unlike_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_like_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_like_icon_name} 失败")

            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"点赞+收藏后_{timestamp}.png", region=self.page)

            """收藏 collect"""
            collect_status = self.page.get_element(business_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

            # 先判断是否是 未收藏
            if collect_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_src]:
                # 如果是未收藏 先收藏 collect
                uncollect_icon = self.page.get_element(business_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                uncollect_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_collect_status = self.page.get_element(business_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_collect_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_collect_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_name} 失败")

                time.sleep(1)
            else:
                # 如果是已收藏 取消收藏
                collect_icon = self.page.get_element(business_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                collect_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_collect_status = self.page.get_element(business_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_collect_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_collect_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_collect_icon_name} 失败")

            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"点赞+收藏后_{timestamp}.png", region=self.page)

        except Exception as e:
            self.logger.error(f"点赞、收藏失败：{str(e)}")
            # 异常时截图
            self.capture(f"点赞、收藏失败_{time.strftime('%H%M%S')}.png")
            raise

        time.sleep(2)
